{"tid":445673,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"中學個陣 總有女同學講到自己條仔好完美","createTime":"2017-10-23T14:49:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T01:10:45.000Z","uid":17677,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"142839cfe460aff690297f2db346e34a3fae3aaf","tid":445673,"uid":17677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:49:16.000Z","msg":"係同一班總會有女同學同外面既男仔拍拖<br />\n而每次都哂命話條仔買野俾佢  又講到條仔好靚仔 <br />\n總之就講到好撚完美   <br />\n最撚西係話我地依啲男同學肥矮柒窮毒 望都唔會望上眼<br />\n唔知以為佢條仔係彭于晏 吳彥祖<br />\n咁其實我都唔想知 但女人總要威 驚死人唔知<br />\n但有一次係街撞到個女同學拖住條仔<br />\n條仔又肥又多暗倉 仲要擔住支煙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲女人咁既審美眼光真係唔怪得依家連G Dragon都話靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261ffe612db0071ed99138a10cd8d09449de0692","tid":445673,"uid":20448,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:59:02.000Z","msg":"暗瘡肥仔有女 咁你呢？"},{"pid":"019ab266e5ff10cf7bf0e0625d8c7e0828192ae5","tid":445673,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:59:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>暗瘡肥仔有女 咁你呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用起底功能啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c62ec8ff6c608d37118e72585c366a100f654901","tid":445673,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:00:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>暗瘡肥仔有女 咁你呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用起底功能啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講緊中學果陣啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65675924b9e62b0afa6f0ab4152262d29d6303d","tid":445673,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:08:00.000Z","msg":"女人的虛榮心是無限大的"},{"pid":"b05cf92fb1518fb3316ad0b07af969dc5a108759","tid":445673,"uid":17677,"like":0